channel.title: Edgeville Autocooker
channel.description:
It says in the name.
Edit: Fine, if u really need details, but the [Req] is not needed because this "is" the request section.
1.You must have your desired raw food in the 1st slot of your bank. 2.The script will withdraw all (28) and walk to the stove west of the bank. 3.Since the door and fence automatically closes after a few minutes, an auto door and fence opener. 4.Using the fish on the stove and cook all, also will occationaly right click just so it wont log out. 5.Walking back to the bank (Auto door and fence opener again) 6.Banking and depositing all and repeat.
[u]Additional and Reminding Details[/u] The fence and door automatically closes in around 5 minutes. Anti-ban/Anti-random event Stops automatically if the color/detail of the raw food in the 1st slot changes (in case you cooked all raws, if... possible...) and log out.
